{{Quote|I was Merellis, a come-up flector for a swoop gang on Caprioril.|[[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] to [[Tionne Solusar|Tionne]]|<ref name="JVS">[[Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force (real-life book)|''Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force'']]</ref>}}
'''Come-up flector''' was a term, possibly originating on [[Caprioril]], for a person who worked [[Spaceport/Legends|starports]] or other points of debarkation, searching for potential buyers of products or services the buyer did not really need.

[[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] posed as such a person under the alias '[[Mara Jade Skywalker|Merellis]]'.<ref name="JVS" />

[[Fleck (Human)|Fleck]], a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]], was the chief come-up flector working for the [[Krish (species)/Legends|Krish]] [[Gamgalon]] on [[Varonat/Legends|Varonat]].<ref name="FC">{{JournalCite|1|First Contact}}</ref>

